    "narrativeArc": "The video explains 7 psychological reasons why a woman returns after a man gives her space. It starts by illustrating common relationship dynamics and then introduces each reason with visual metaphors and diagrams. The narrative progresses from identifying problems (chasing, feeding ego) to explaining the psychological mechanisms (emotional vacuums, reactance theory, emotional memory) that make a woman chase, emphasizing the power of silence and unpredictability. It concludes by highlighting that women seek emotional authorship and control over the narrative, which is disrupted by a man's strategic distance."
